{"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"case"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion"},{"code":[" If a text's language supports horizontal writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out horizontally."],"type":"codeListing","syntax":null}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal":{"title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"title":"MLNTextWritingMode","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingMode"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant."}],"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","role":"collection"}}}